In this report the sales and revenue is represented monthly and weekly. 
This report consists 
1) line chart - This line chart shows important key metrics(i-Occupancy, ii-Average daily rate, iii- RevPar AKA revenue per available room) on weekly basis
2) Bar chart - This bar chart shows the percentage of revenue generated and ADR from booking platforms
3)Pie chart - This pie chart shows the percentage of revenue generated from room categories i.e.., Luxury or Business
4)A scroll down filters to adjust as convenience such as i)Filter by city , ii)Filter by Room type , iii) Filter by month and week
5)tabular data comprising key metrics and their corresponding fluctuations, delineating the variations observed in each metric with changes applied to the specified filter parameters.



